{"messageId": "1516998d87d4b369", "headers": {"From": "Matt Ikle <matt.ikle@gmail.com>", "Date": "Thu, 3 Dec 2015 13:46:40 -0700", "Subject": "Re: [opencog-dev] Errata PLN book?"}, "body": "I think that the b_i/2 are the tails and that 1-b_i is the center of the distribution. I.E. b=.05 would mean each tail would have area .025."},
